#2585 added "this.foo" however a standalone "this" doesn't work, e.g.

```
class ...
   function string get_s;
      // %p does NOT include parameter values
      return $sformatf("%p", this);
   endfunction

module ...
   initial $display("%s", o.get_s());

```
@rkapuscik perhaps you'd be willing to contribute this?
